                <h1>Annie Musical: A Timeless Tale of Hope and Adventure</h1>
                <p>Annie is a beloved musical that tells the uplifting story of a young orphan named Annie, who dreams of finding her parents. Set during the Great Depression, her adventures lead her to billionaire Oliver Warbucks, who changes her life forever. With memorable songs like "Tomorrow," Annie's tale of hope and resilience continues to inspire audiences worldwide.</p>
